        <h2>Filtering unpriced Variants for new sites</h2>
        <p>A system policy labeled <span class="Emphasis">Filter unpriced Variants for New Site Pricing</span> controls whether the <span class="Emphasis">New Site Pricing</span> utility in Site Manager returns all Variants or only those with prices for the selected Price Type (Regular, Promotion, etc.). The default for the system policy is <span class="Emphasis">False</span> meaning all Variants for the selected price type display. If the system policy is set to <span class="Emphasis">True</span>, then only Variants with a price for the selected price type display.</p>
    </body>
</html>